<h2 id="key-features">🔧 Key Features for Real Estate Operators</h2>

<h3>Automated Drip Campaigns</h3>

Long-term nurture sequences keep you top-of-mind with leads who aren't ready to transact. We configure 12-18 month campaigns mixing market updates, property alerts, and value-add content. When leads re-engage—opening emails, clicking links—automation can escalate them back to active follow-up.

<h3>Appointment Scheduling</h3>

Built-in calendar booking eliminates the back-and-forth of scheduling showings or consultations. Integration with Google Calendar prevents double-booking, automated reminders reduce no-shows, and team calendars enable round-robin assignment for incoming appointments.

<h3>Document Management</h3>

While not a replacement for dedicated transaction management platforms like Dotloop or SkySlope, GoHighLevel handles standard document collection and e-signatures for intake forms, buyer questionnaires, and similar high-volume documents.

<h3>Reporting and Analytics</h3>

Pipeline reporting shows conversion rates between stages, identifying where deals stall. Marketing analytics track lead source performance, helping operators double down on channels that deliver quality leads and cut spend on underperformers.

