<h2 id="supporting-tools">🛠️ Supporting Tools for Complete Stack</h2>

While GoHighLevel handles CRM and marketing automation, complete real estate operations require additional specialized tools:

<h3>Transaction Management</h3>

Dotloop or SkySlope remain superior for document-heavy transaction coordination, especially for compliance-focused brokerages. These integrate with GoHighLevel through Zapier, syncing deal status back to your CRM pipelines.

<h3>Property Analysis</h3>

For investors, DealMachine handles driving-for-dollars lead generation with skip tracing integration. PropStream or BatchLeads provide property data and owner information for direct mail and outbound campaigns. Both integrate via API or Zapier to push leads into GoHighLevel for nurture sequences.

<h3>Financial Management</h3>

Stessa (free for basic use) handles rental property bookkeeping and reporting. For more complex portfolios, AppFolio or Buildium provide full property management capabilities including tenant portals, maintenance tracking, and owner reporting.

<h3>Marketing Creative</h3>

Canva Pro ($13/month) handles listing graphics, social content, and marketing materials. For video walkthroughs, Loom or BombBomb integrate video messaging into your outreach sequences.

